item.title: 【Albums (lossy)】Dolby AC-4 - Taylor Swift - Red [Dolby AC-4 Immersive Stereo]
item.description:
Upmixing process:
Stereo FLAC → Normalized loudness to -18 LUFS and manually declipped in Adobe Audtion → 2.0 to 7.1.2 upmix in Nuendo → Exported as Dolby Atmos Master (ADM) → Converted to AC-4 with Dolby Media Encoder
